Looking at the problem, the relevant section is under "Cash and Cash Equivalents". The line item "Ending Balance" provides the value of cash and cash equivalents at the end of the period. 

From the table:
- "Ending Balance" is listed as "6885735.26" on the date "2024-02-05".

Therefore, the value of cash and cash equivalents at the end of the period is "6885735.26".

The solution in the required JSON format is:

```json
{"solution": {'value': '6885735.26'} }
```
